data.description: WOW! What a beautiful transformation. Centrally located. 1.19 acres, the owners have meticulously remodeled this one of a kind 3 bedroom, 2 bath home. The expense of installation makes owning a home with a large in-ground pool a rare find in our local market. The pool is surrounded by lush foliage in the spring and summer months, and a newly hand built covered awning giving room for enjoying outdoor space. Moving inside, the owners have added numerous updates including: Luxury vinyl floors and base molding throughout, both bathrooms have been gutted and completely modernized, white buffet style cabinets were added and topped with Sparrows Peak butcher block, the kitchen island counter has been revamped with a rich pine butcher block and a new dishwasher installed, new closet doors and shelving, custom blinds, new light fixtures, the gas log fireplace has been given a stunning face lift, and every room freshly painted in custom colors. The exterior has been painted, new landscaping added, and thousands spent on tree removal. A storage building will convey with the sale. The right side of the property is large enough and could be ideal to add garage/shop.
